title: GirlsWay - Marie McCray, Karlie Montana (What Weve Lost: Part On
description:
Karlie Montana cant deal with her recent breakup with Marie McCray. The pain of picking up her stuff is too much for her to bare, going crazy inside, not knowing how to cope with it. The pain is surreal, and she wishes she could wake up from this nightmare, but she knows she has to face reality, picking up the last of her items at a place she used to call home. She sits on the bed, reminiscing at pictures of her and Marie, now a distant and painful memory. But all hell breaks loose when Marie walks into the bedroom.
